g and detecting Alzheimer&#8217;s earlier. Alzheimer&#8217;s prediction and=
 detection have also come along way. </p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55)=
; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Blood-based biom=
arkers like amyloid-beta and tau proteins have become accurate enough for c=
linical use. These tests identify the presence of Alzheimer&#8217;s patholo=
gy before symptoms appear, enabling early intervention.</p><p style=3D"colo=
r: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;=
"><span>AI can enhance the analysis of MRI and PET scans, improving the ide=
